{"pageProps":{"note":{"id":"kWFdZQuRbvz7uwXfqCA8n","title":"Nrf52840","desc":"","updated":1644729955555,"created":1644491156028,"stub":true,"custom":{"stub":true},"fname":"ee.nrf52840","type":"note","vault":{"fsPath":"vault"},"contentHash":"b39a66f0e2c734f60425b63296bd7339","links":[{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"ee.nrf52840","id":"kWFdZQuRbvz7uwXfqCA8n","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.zephyr.bindings","alias":"ee.zephyr.bindings","position":{"start":{"line":16,"column":1,"offset":229},"end":{"line":16,"column":23,"offset":251},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.zephyr.bindings"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"ee.nrf52840","id":"kWFdZQuRbvz7uwXfqCA8n","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.zephyr.device-tree","alias":"ee.zephyr.device-tree","position":{"start":{"line":18,"column":83,"offset":335},"end":{"line":18,"column":108,"offset":360},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.zephyr.device-tree"}},{"type":"wiki","from":{"fname":"ee.nrf52840","id":"kWFdZQuRbvz7uwXfqCA8n","vaultName":"vault"},"value":"ee.zephyr","alias":"ee.zephyr","position":{"start":{"line":60,"column":1,"offset":1538},"end":{"line":60,"column":14,"offset":1551},"indent":[]},"xvault":false,"sameFile":false,"to":{"fname":"ee.zephyr"}},{"from":{"fname":"ee.hw.solar-charging","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":30,"column":120,"offset":2035},"end":{"line":30,"column":135,"offset":2050},"indent":[]},"value":"ee.nrf52840","alias":"ee.nrf52840"},{"from":{"fname":"ee.hw.usb-isolation","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":9,"column":3,"offset":664},"end":{"line":9,"column":18,"offset":679},"indent":[]},"value":"ee.nrf52840","alias":"ee.nrf52840"},{"from":{"fname":"ee.nrf52840.zb.power-consumption","vaultName":"vault"},"type":"backlink","position":{"start":{"line":26,"column":87,"offset":1157},"end":{"line":26,"column":102,"offset":1172},"indent":[]},"value":"ee.nrf52840","alias":"ee.nrf52840"}],"anchors":{},"children":["HjwogFUd6N0ZqABEfP2QT","UTyVZZrIY615EpsVASnyB","9MyAYKhCMZKoZjGva2vS3"],"parent":"SEWMNyq5ejB4Uu2o5gD1F","data":{}},"body":"<h1 id=\"nrf52840\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#nrf52840\"></a>Nrf52840</h1>\n<h2 id=\"datasheet\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#datasheet\"></a>Datasheet</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://infocenter.nordicsemi.com/pdf/nRF52840_PS_v1.1.pdf\">https://infocenter.nordicsemi.com/pdf/nRF52840_PS_v1.1.pdf</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"617-pwm\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#617-pwm\"></a>6.17 PWM</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>4 PWM Channels</li>\n<li>Can PWM be used on any GPIO?</li>\n</ul>\n<h4 id=\"pwm-zephyr-bindings\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#pwm-zephyr-bindings\"></a>PWM Zephyr Bindings</h4>\n<p><a href=\"/notes/notes/QbIzU99Iv6L01tKB2QbDb\">Bindings</a></p>\n<p>The <code>chn-pin</code> (<code>n=0,1,2,3</code>) properties are a little confusing. As an example, the <a href=\"/notes/notes/CXH9VVDqIEHZvwL6XAckJ\">Device Tree</a> for the dongle straightforwardly sets <code>ch0-pin = &#x3C; 0x8 ></code> to map channel 0 to to pin <code>P0.8</code>. In contrast, <code>ch1-pin = &#x3C; 0x29 ></code> maps to pin <code>P1.9</code>:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><code class=\"language-js\">    <span class=\"token literal-property property\">pwm0</span><span class=\"token operator\">:</span> pwm@4001c000 <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        compatible <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"nordic,nrf-pwm\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        reg <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x4001c000</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x1000</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        interrupts <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x1c</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        status <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"okay\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        label <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"PWM_0\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        #pwm<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>cells <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x1</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        ch0<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x8</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        ch0<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>inverted<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        ch1<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x29</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        ch1<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>inverted<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        ch2<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>pin <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0xc</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        ch2<span class=\"token operator\">-</span>inverted<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n        phandle <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&#x3C;</span> <span class=\"token number\">0x5</span> <span class=\"token operator\">></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>The note on <code>ch0-pin</code> in <a href=\"https://developer.nordicsemi.com/nRF_Connect_SDK/doc/latest/zephyr/reference/devicetree/bindings/pwm/nordic%2Cnrf-pwm.html#dtbinding-nordic-nrf-pwm\">nordic,nrf-pwm - Zephyr Project Documentation</a> explains the difference in mappings:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>The channel 0 pin to use.</p>\n<p>For pins P0.0 through P0.31, use the pin number. For example,\nto use P0.16 for channel 0, set:</p>\n<p>ch0-pin = &#x3C;16>;</p>\n<p>For pins P1.0 through P1.31, add 32 to the pin number. For\nexample, to use P1.2 for channel 0, set:</p>\n<p>ch0-pin = &#x3C;34>;  /<em> 32 + 2 </em>/</p>\n</blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"7-hardware-and-layout\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#7-hardware-and-layout\"></a>7 Hardware and layout</h3>\n<h4 id=\"71-pin-assignment\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#71-pin-assignment\"></a>7.1 Pin assignment</h4>\n<p>p 576</p>\n<h2 id=\"zephyr\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#zephyr\"></a>Zephyr</h2>\n<p><a href=\"/notes/notes/qoWNfMZ0oqJ0T3ag3HFaR\">Zephyr</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"bindings-documentation\"><a aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"anchor-heading icon-link\" href=\"#bindings-documentation\"></a>Bindings Documentation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://developer.nordicsemi.com/nRF_Connect_SDK/doc/latest/zephyr/reference/devicetree/bindings/pwm/nordic%2Cnrf-pwm.html#dtbinding-nordic-nrf-pwm\">nordic,nrf-pwm - Zephyr Project Documentation</a></p>\n<hr>\n<strong>Children</strong>\n<ol>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/notes/HjwogFUd6N0ZqABEfP2QT\">Dev Kit</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/notes/UTyVZZrIY615EpsVASnyB\">Dongle</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/notes/notes/9MyAYKhCMZKoZjGva2vS3\">ZigBee</a></li>\n</ol>\n<hr>\n<strong>Backlinks</strong>\n<ul